<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>더뷰티풀 - 이미지 파일 업로드</title>
<style type="text/css">
#submit, #reset{display: none;}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>사진등록</h1>
<p>이미지 파일만 업로드 가능</p>
<form action="/theviewtiful/file-upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" onreset="initSrc()">
<input type="file" accept="image/*" id="file" onchange="fileSizeChecker(event)"><span id="fileSize">파일사이즈</span><br>
<img id="output" width="500px"/>
<input type="submit" value="업로드" id="submit">
<input type="reset" value="삭제" id="reset">
</form>
<script type="text/javascript" src="profil-picture-upload.js"></script>
</body>
</html>